{"tid":2140634,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"你地屋企窗外睇唔睇到其它屋入面 d 野？","createTime":"2020-08-05T06:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T11:04:27.000Z","uid":5218,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a65f0638b7db515f0ffdcc96ae71730ae5e2cb45","tid":2140634,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:27:28.000Z","msg":"我住緊𠴱度廚房窗離遠係可以望斜對面單位既露台位，基本上可以睇哂屋入面既，間唔間中會睇到屋內條女帶住個 bra 或赤裸向廁所行入房或向房行返入廁所，有時佢又會飛哂釘向露台位度煲煙剪腳甲。"},{"pid":"9bca4da21ed9ab38d40f90848651a31d1a391999","tid":2140634,"uid":5649,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:28:41.000Z","msg":"屋企對面係墳場"},{"pid":"5795a26ccb5f87bf8bb1c7525459c645458564c6","tid":2140634,"uid":334765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:31:45.000Z","msg":"廳有個細對流窗對住天井可以望到對面屋個對流窗甚至入面"},{"pid":"02099d485bc784705f17dd6e597ec36203cb3c17","tid":2140634,"uid":154817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:13:47.000Z","msg":"你老母住隔離屋仲要戴bra比你睇？"},{"pid":"2ffa28a453cb879317a8b916906d4cc60be12440","tid":2140634,"uid":32442,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:16:30.000Z","msg":"換衫除衫下下都要拉窗簾<br />\n好攰個時會諗如果呢個世界無男人就唔駛咁麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc333e53b5d6bdcd7052343947ce870681f91dab","tid":2140634,"uid":335664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:46:22.000Z","msg":"圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283a2f0e96b6f8b14d0208aeae98b1e8f375848c","tid":2140634,"uid":237538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:27:38.000Z","msg":"哇屌 你放盤寫明應該可以叫高10%<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bbc8ff1b9cc17acd0416edc0d83ae3276121a85","tid":2140634,"uid":134636,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:39:39.000Z","msg":"見到人地啲傢俬行來行去都見到，不過唔係好清楚<br />\n<br />\n細個對眼好攰望下街景休息下對眼，見到對面曬衫，佢望到我企係窗邊，我覺得突然縮入屋好似我特登裝佢又好尷尬咁唔知點好，跟住我對佢揮揮手，佢呆左一呆又對我揮手，最後我覺得好柒閂左窗簾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個棟樓都隔左半條街，剩係見到個人同衣著，見唔同樣好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff066c363a6c8bfccc1ce2cd45a475ac5575e27","tid":2140634,"uid":127044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a65f0638b7db515f0ffdcc96ae71730ae5e2cb45","tid":2140634,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:27:28.000Z","msg":"我住緊𠴱度廚房窗離遠係可以望斜對面單位既露台位，基本上可以睇哂屋入面既，間唔間中會睇到屋內條女帶住個 bra 或赤裸向廁所行入房或向房行返入廁所，有時佢又會飛哂釘向露台位度煲煙剪腳甲。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:48:18.000Z","msg":"邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b9ab83fb94775d95ba30517660a96e3ced476b","tid":2140634,"uid":311267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:49:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91ecc9bce2d71f2c497bcda8881d43ea15b5ff34","tid":2140634,"uid":8528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:52:06.000Z","msg":"依個post諗起以前高登/連登 ，成日post 影到對面大廈赤裸打J 嘅男人相"},{"pid":"b1354ae25b1f82394386a6b6170c52fb3ffae5a2","tid":2140634,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:53:14.000Z","msg":"無哂幻想<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da8a7ddf92a1bc87792f958939c19ba465948ae","tid":2140634,"uid":207991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"91ecc9bce2d71f2c497bcda8881d43ea15b5ff34","tid":2140634,"uid":8528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:52:06.000Z","msg":"依個post諗起以前高登/連登 ，成日post 影到對面大廈赤裸打J 嘅男人相"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:56:04.000Z","msg":"seed"},{"pid":"edf1db3f47dd2b14fb14d7b87b86fbe15e548cd6","tid":2140634,"uid":66701